{"tid":1055831,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"谷m谷到個人好辛苦","createTime":"2019-03-10T18:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T09:38:40.000Z","uid":133438,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3a99a314fa827800392154d6eb589aa0c2ef3784","tid":1055831,"uid":133438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:43:27.000Z","msg":"我近一年經期都唔太準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢大半年開始都有keep住睇中醫調理 但都好似差唔多咁 每個月都遲黎幾日 有血塊 個人谷m個陣都好猛陣 <br />\n<br />\n呢個月仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲19天氣又濕又冷又熱搞到個人成日病 依家遲左成一星期都未黎m<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又keep住喉嚨痛作感冒胸脹肚脹失眠便秘咁 好辛苦呀真係 有冇絲打可以幫下我呀 想快啲黎到m唔洗再受苦 都唔知邊個發明女人要黎m呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：依家訓唔撚到出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4431d546daad5e841ef252589d4f5d0b32bf60c2","tid":1055831,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"我都係 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d221dfc5f484a55d4a14249b35b1113081319757","tid":1055831,"uid":133438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:45:35.000Z","msg":"不過興幸自己都只係谷m個期辛苦 黎m唔會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲絲打真係見住佢痛到面容扭曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee71d40b88b011441c4d882701d0f2f4b22df63","tid":1055831,"uid":133438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4431d546daad5e841ef252589d4f5d0b32bf60c2","tid":1055831,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0